{
  "stem": "1415.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] To get out of here because they're going to take me away if I don't get out of here.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I made myself disappear.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And I-- I-- I went, and I-- I tried to find another hiding place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] While I was looking for that other-- finding the other place, a Ukrainian soldier, who was like a German-- in those days, you know, they were all even worse than the Germans-- he stopped me.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I knew my goose was cooked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I-- I didn't have a chance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Because he stopped me, and-- and it must have been at the end of the day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And he took me over to where a group of women formed to go off to the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And he-- he brought me there, and he identified himself to-- to the German SS [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] who was leading-- leading that group.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And at that group, there was also the head of our camp was there, the Jewish head of our camp was there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And there were a lot of other people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But the group itself was all women.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And while he was identifying himself to the SS and telling him about me, my mother saw me in the group.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And she pulled me into the group.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And where the SS man asked him where-- he was looking around for me, because he had told him something or another.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "I wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this time, the SS had a big poke in his hand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he went amongst the women, and he just went with the poke, and he hit everybody on the side, on each side, until he got to me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother was holding onto my hand.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
